instructions.mintCredits: Use one of the project IDs above with: sui client call --package <PACKAGE_ID> --module carbon_credit --function mint_credits --args <DEVELOPER_CAP_ID> <PROJECT_ID> <AMOUNT> '{}' --gas-budget 100000000
instructions.createListing: After minting credits, create a listing with: sui client call --package <PACKAGE_ID> --module carbon_credit --function create_listing --args <CREDIT_ID> <PRICE_IN_SUI> --gas-budget 100000000
instructions.findCredits: Run: sui client objects <YOUR_ADDRESS> | grep CarbonCredit
instructions.findListings: Run: sui client objects <YOUR_ADDRESS> | grep CreditListing
